---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const pageTitle = "Reserva Confirmada | Katy Caballero Osteópata";
const pageDescription = "Tu reserva ha sido recibida. Toda la información que necesitas antes de tu cita de osteopatía en Alpedrete.";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} noindex={true} breadcrumbs={[{ name: "Inicio", url: "/" }, { name: "Reservar", url: "/reservar" }, { name: "Confirmación" }]}>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="check-icon">
        <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
          <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1>Solicitud recibida</h1>
      <p>Gracias por confiar en mí. He recibido tu solicitud de cita correctamente.</p>
      <div class="pending-notice" role="note">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        <div>
          <strong>Pendiente de confirmación</strong>
          <span>Me pondré en contacto contigo por <strong>WhatsApp o teléfono</strong> lo antes posible para confirmar la cita.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="booking-details" class="booking-details" style="display:none;"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
    const servicio = params.get('servicio');
    const fecha = params.get('fecha');
    const hora = params.get('hora');
    const precio = params.get('precio');
    if (servicio && fecha && hora) {
      const el = document.getElementById('booking-details')!;
      el.style.display = 'block';
      el.innerHTML = `
        <div class="detail-row"><span>Servicio</span><strong>${servicio}</strong></div>
        <div class="detail-row"><span>Fecha</span><strong>${fecha}</strong></div>
        <div class="detail-row"><span>Hora</span><strong>${hora}</strong></div>
        ${precio ? `<div class="detail-row"><span>Precio</span><strong>${precio}</strong></div>` : ''}
      `;
    }
  </script>

  <section class="info-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Antes de venir</span>
        <h2>Información útil</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 003 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0021 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Que traer</h3>
          <p>Ven con <strong>ropa comoda</strong>. Si es tu primera visita, trae tu historial medico o informes recientes si los tienes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Como llegar</h3>
          <p>C/ Rio Guadarrama 2, Alpedrete.<br><strong>Parking gratuito</strong> en la puerta.</p>
          <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Calle+Rio+Guadarrama+2+Alpedrete+Madrid" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card-link">Ver en Google Maps</a>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 015.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Tu primera visita</h3>
          <p>Conoce como sera tu primera sesion: valoracion, tratamiento y recomendaciones.</p>
          <a href="/primera-visita" class="card-link">Ver guia primera visita</a>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 01-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 014.11 2h3a2 2 0 012 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 00.7 2.81 2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 002.81.7A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Contacto</h3>
          <p>Teléfono: <a href="tel:+34643961065">643 961 065</a></p>
          <a href="https://wa.me/34643961065" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card-link">Escribir por WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="meanwhile-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Recursos</span>
        <h2>Mientras tanto...</h2>
        <p>Aprovecha la espera con contenido que puede ayudarte.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="meanwhile-grid">
        <a href="/blog" class="meanwhile-card">
          <div class="meanwhile-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 014 4v14a3 3 0 00-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 00-4 4v14a3 3 0 013-3h7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Blog de salud</h3>
          <p>Articulos sobre osteopatia, bienestar y habitos saludables.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/guia-estiramientos" class="meanwhile-card">
          <div class="meanwhile-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 20V10"/><path d="M12 20V4"/><path d="M6 20v-6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Guia de estiramientos</h3>
          <p>Ejercicios sencillos para mejorar tu movilidad desde casa.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cancel-note">
    <div class="container">
      <p>Si necesitas <strong>cancelar o cambiar tu cita</strong>, contactame por <a href="https://wa.me/34643961065" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a> o llamando al <a href="tel:+34643961065">643 961 065</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding-top: 150px;
    padding-bottom: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-cream) 0%, var(--color-warm-white) 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 600px;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  .pending-notice {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 28px auto 0;
    background: #fff8e6;
    border: 1px solid #e8c97a;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-secondary, #c4a35a);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    color: #5a4a1f;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .pending-notice svg {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #8b6f30;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .pending-notice strong { display: block; color: #5a4a1f; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .pending-notice span { display: block; color: #6b5a2c; }
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .pending-notice {
    background: rgba(196, 163, 90, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(196, 163, 90, 0.35);
    color: #e8dcc4;
  }
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .pending-notice strong { color: #f0e4cc; }
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .pending-notice span { color: #d4c8ac; }
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .pending-notice svg { color: #e8c97a; }

  .booking-details {
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 30px auto 0;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 124, 89, 0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .detail-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .detail-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .detail-row span {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .detail-row strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .check-icon {
    width: 90px;
    height: 90px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 25px;
    color: white;
    animation: scaleIn 0.5s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes scaleIn {
    0% {
      transform: scale(0);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    60% {
      transform: scale(1.15);
    }
    100% {
      transform: scale(1);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  /* Info Section */
  .info-section {
    background: var(--color-warm-white);
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 25px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .info-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 35px 25px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 124, 89, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .info-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(90, 124, 89, 0.12);
  }

  .info-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--color-secondary-light);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .info-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .info-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .info-card p a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .card-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 12px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Meanwhile Section */
  .meanwhile-section {
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .meanwhile-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .meanwhile-card {
    background: var(--color-warm-white);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px 30px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 124, 89, 0.1);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: block;
  }

  .meanwhile-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(90, 124, 89, 0.12);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .meanwhile-icon {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    background: var(--color-secondary-light);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .meanwhile-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .meanwhile-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: none;
  }

  /* Cancel Note */
  .cancel-note {
    background: var(--color-warm-white);
    padding: 40px 0;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(90, 124, 89, 0.1);
  }

  .cancel-note p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cancel-note a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cancel-note a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 450px;
    }

    .meanwhile-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 450px;
    }
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .booking-details {
    background: #2a2a3e;
    border-color: rgba(111, 155, 110, 0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .detail-row {
    border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .detail-row span {
    color: #aaa;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .detail-row strong {
    color: #e0e0e0;
  }

  /* Dark mode overrides */
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .info-card {
    background: #2a2a3e;
    border-color: rgba(111, 155, 110, 0.12);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .info-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .meanwhile-card {
    border-color: rgba(111, 155, 110, 0.12);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .meanwhile-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .cancel-note {
    border-top-color: rgba(111, 155, 110, 0.12);
  }
</style>
